        "content": "<p>What is the best practice for implementing a work queue design pattern in Lean?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">Queue</span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">queue</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">new</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ArrayDeque</span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;&gt;</span><span class=\"o\">()</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span>\n<span class=\"n\">queue</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">add</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span>\n<span class=\"n\">while</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">!</span><span class=\"n\">queue</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">isEmpty</span><span class=\"o\">())</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">process</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">queue</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">poll</span><span class=\"o\">(),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">queue</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">//</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">adds</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">to</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">queue</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n<span class=\"n\">next</span><span class=\"o\">()</span><span class=\"bp\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">//</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">continue</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">execution</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"